    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior paint retains a nice luster, though there are some minor stone chips on the front bumper and light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and floor mats. All electronics and mechanical components are functioning as intended, and the car drives smoothly. This is a reliable, solid vehicle that presents very well for its age and mileage.",
      "price": 34500.0,
