    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality example that has been pampered since day one. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining a deep, mirror-like finish with zero scratches or dings, while the interior remains in pristine, 'like-new' state with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with all service records available. Buyers can expect a vehicle that looks, smells, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
